cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "epc: Ensemble-Preserving Compression of MD trajectories with a kinetic bound"
abstract: >-
  An analysis-native compressor for molecular-dynamics trajectories that unifies a
  normalizing-flow density, a Markov-state dynamics model, and entropy coding under one
  path-distribution (KL/Pinsker) guarantee, providing a fidelity bound on kinetic
  observables (the part static/ensemble bounds do not cover).
type: software
authors:
